CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

January 24, 2011

[Cite as 01/24/2011 Case Announcements #2, 2011-Ohio-266.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2011-0064. State ex rel. King v. Court of Appeals, Ninth Appellate Dist.

In Prohibition. This cause originated in this court on the filing of a complaint for a writ of prohibition.

Upon review of the complaint, it is ordered by the court, sua sponte, that respondents shall file them response to the complaint no later than Friday, January 28, 2011.
